text.tspan: Meat consumption vs. GDP per capita, 2013
Average meat consumption per capita, measured in kilograms per year versus gross domestic product (GDP) per capita measured
in 2011 international-$. International-$ corrects for price differences across countries. Figures do not include fish or seafood.
